      "description": "This is a true time-capsule specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, retaining its original factory luster. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple and crease-free, the carpets are pristine, and that signature new-car scent is still present. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history documenting every scheduled maintenance interval. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with precision. This sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. For the discerning collector who demands perfection, this vehicle stands as the definitive example.",
